CHANGES_pyq_supabase.md

# Examin8 Last Year Papers fetch cache — heavy (per-paper snapshot HTML, ~140MB).
# The DB (papers table, class_level=10) is the source of truth; these are a
# regenerable cache from scripts/examin8/fetchClass10LastYearPapers.js. The small
# catalog (metadata only) IS tracked as the record of what was imported.
data/examin8/*/raw/last-year-papers/
data/examin8/*/normalized/last-year-papers.json

# Examin8 NCERT/Exemplar textbook fetch cache — regenerable per-node raw pages.
# The DB (ncert_solutions, className='Class 10') is the source of truth; the small
# normalized ncert-solutions.json IS tracked as the import record.
data/examin8/*/raw/ncert/

# Examin8 Class 10 question-bank fetch cache (Important Qs / PYQ / Practice) — raw
# pages are regenerable; DB (sections+questions) is the source of truth. Normalized
# JSON is kept small enough to track as the import record.
data/examin8/*/raw/important_questions/
data/examin8/*/raw/pyq/
data/examin8/*/raw/practice/

# Examin8 Class 10 question-bank normalized JSON — large (full question+solution HTML).
# DB (sections+questions) is the source of truth; regenerable via fetchClass10Questions.js.
data/examin8/*/normalized/important_questions.json
data/examin8/*/normalized/pyq.json
data/examin8/*/normalized/practice.json

# Examin8 Class 10 Mock Tests fetch cache — raw graded-result JSON + large normalized.
# DB (mock_tests + mock_test_questions, class_level=10) is the source of truth.
data/examin8/*/raw/mock-tests/
data/examin8/*/normalized/mock-tests.json

data/examin8/*/normalized/ncert-solutions.json
